#tr.en: May I add the wealth that (is) at your right (side). May I achieve the favor that (is) at [your] left.

14. qi₂-bi-ma liš-še-me₂ zik-ri#
#tr.en: Command that my utterance be heard.

15. a-mat a-qab-bu-u₂ ki-ma a-qab-bu-u₂ lu-u₂ ma-ag-rat
